  <walkingGeneralDescription><![CDATA[<p>On an Inghams walking holiday, you have the freedom to explore the area at your own pace. Each day, a new adventure, with as much or as little walking as you like.</p>
<h3>Why we love walking holidays in Lech</h3>
<p>A true walker's paradise, Lech's 350 kilometres of marked hiking paths range from flower-filled meadows, riverside and woodland paths starting from the village centre, to remote high alpine routes up to beautiful lakes and rugged peaks. There are plenty of rustic mountain alms, as well as designated picnic areas, and a great sense of travel as paths link through local hamlets and over into different valleys.</p>
<h3>Guided Walks</h3>
<p>Guided walks are offered through the Lech Summer Card, including themed herbal and history walks and a twilight hike. <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/hotels/item91731/austria/" target="_blank">Hotel Austria</a> also offers free guided walks with their own walking guides - subject to change at short notice.</p>]]></walkingGeneralDescription>
